Sentencas: In order to identify new cathode compositions for the high temperature solid oxide fuel cell, we have investigated the effect of the trivalent cations Al and Ga at the Mn site of the well-studied cathode composition La0.84Sr0.16MnO3.
Titulo: New cathode compositions based on La0.84Sr0.16Mn1-xMxO3, where M = Al, Ga for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: All the compositions have been prepared by the low temperature citrate-nitrate auto-ignition process and sintered within the temperature range of 1150-1350 degrees C for 4 h.
Titulo: New cathode compositions based on La0.84Sr0.16Mn1-xMxO3, where M = Al, Ga for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In order to understand the compatibility of the prepared samples as alternative cathode materials, we compared their electrical conductivity and thermal expansion coefficient with those of La0.84Sr0.16MnO3 and yttria-stabilized zirconia.
Titulo: New cathode compositions based on La0.84Sr0.16Mn1-xMxO3, where M = Al, Ga for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A 10 mol% Al doped La0.84Sr0.16MnO3 composition exhibited a conductivity of around 122 S cm(-1) at 950 degrees C and a thermal expansion coefficient of 11.04 x 10(-6)
Titulo: New cathode compositions based on La0.84Sr0.16Mn1-xMxO3, where M = Al, Ga for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: K with a minimum reactivity towards yttria-stabilized zirconia.
Titulo: New cathode compositions based on La0.84Sr0.16Mn1-xMxO3, where M = Al, Ga for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Though the conductivity of the new composition is lower than that of La0.84Sr0.16MnO3 (169 S cm(-1) at 950 degrees C), it is still high enough for use as a cathode material.
Titulo: New cathode compositions based on La0.84Sr0.16Mn1-xMxO3, where M = Al, Ga for solid oxide fuel cell
